data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!! Clean & Spacious 1274 sqft, 3Brm/2Bth home has been completely Refreshed & Refurbished! Perfect for everyday living as well as entertainment: the Open Concept of the main living area flows out to the backyards covered patios and fire pit! The home sits on .34 acres w/mature landscaping, has a detached 2 car garage, plentiful parking w/the long driveway, and still room for your RV too; in the backyard there is a storage barn and lots of space to play and garden in! Home Warranty included! OPEN HOUSE - SATURDAY 12/16/23 from 12pm to 2pm! Join us for Hot Chocolate & sweet treats while you tour this Super Cute and CLEAN property! Enter the raffle for your chance to win a nice Gift Basket!
